snippet.title: Red Alert 2: Yuri's Revenge | Official Trailer - Epic RTS Expansion | AzureDarko
snippet.description:
Prepare for mind control, chaos, and epic battles in the official trailer for Command & Conquer: Red Alert 2 - Yuri's Revenge!
 Witness the rise of Yuri as he unleashes his psychic forces, new units,
 and devastating powers in this iconic RTS expansion. Relive the glory 
of commanding powerful armies and stopping Yuri’s reign of terror!

🎮 Game: Command & Conquer: Red Alert 2 - Yuri's Revenge
🛡️ Content: Official trailer highlighting new units, powers, and gameplay mechanics
🌟 Highlights: Epic battles, mind control mechanics, and strategic depth
